videos.description: Michael Gallup breaks a tackle and streaks for 56 yards to give the Rams the early lead over Nevada.
videos.headline: Colorado State scores first with TD

videos.description: Nick Stevens connects with an open Michael Gallup for a 7-yard touchdown to add to the Rams' lead.
videos.headline: Colorado State pads lead with TD

videos.description: Ty Gangi passes to Trevion Armstrong for a 5- yard touchdown to close the gap.
videos.headline: Nevada chips away at Rams lead with TD

videos.description: Ty Gangi lobs it down the field to a wide open McLane Mannix for a touchdown and the tie.
videos.headline: Mannix ties game with TD

videos.description: Rams' Izzy Matthews find an opening and easily makes his way into the end zone for a 1-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Matthews walks his way into end zone

videos.description: Kelton Moore breaks off tackles and powers his way into the end zone for the touchdown for the Wolf Pack.
videos.headline: Moore rushes 1 yard for TD

videos.description: Rams' Nick Stevens finds Dalton Fackrell in the end zone for a 14-yard touchdown to take back the lead late in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Colorado State reclaims lead with TD

videos.description: Ty Gangi finds Daiyan Henley for a 6-yard touchdown to tie the Rams in the third quarter.
videos.headline: Henley TD ties game in 3rd quarter

videos.description: Ty Gangi throws one deep down the middle to find Wyatt Demps for a 65-yard touchdown for the lead.
videos.headline: Gangi goes deep to take the lead

videos.description: Rams' Dalyn Dawkins turns on the jets and speeds down the field and rushes for a 59-yard touchdown to chip away at Nevada's lead.
videos.headline: Dawkins bursts into the end zone

videos.description: Nick Stevens connects with an open Michael Gallup for his third touchdown of the night,  reclaiming Colorado State's lead in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Gallup grabs third TD of game
